title: iNsurge looking for dia+ jungler for OOL
body:
Hey guys, looking for a dia+ jungler to join our team, very strong laners just need a solid jungler to complete our team. If interested contact me by adding my IGN: Restricted.
Requirements-
Must be active
Needs to be able to talk on discord
Flexible champ pool and a positive attitude :)
